line-height:150%"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;">七、招聘须知<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;
line-height:150%"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;">（一）综合柜员招聘结合绵阳市商业银行<span lang="EN-US">2017</span>年春季招聘相关安排进行，网申截止日期做适当延长。网申：<span lang="EN-US">2017</span>年<span lang="EN-US">3</span>月<span lang="EN-US">29</span>日—<span lang="EN-US">4</span>月<span lang="EN-US">12</span>日，笔面试：<span lang="EN-US">2017</span>年<span lang="EN-US">4</span>月<span lang="EN-US">14</span>日—<span lang="EN-US">4</span>月<span lang="EN-US">17</span>日，体检：<span lang="EN-US">2017</span>年<span lang="EN-US">4</span>月<span lang="EN-US">25</span>日—<span lang="EN-US">4</span>月<span lang="EN-US">30</span>日。<b><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;
line-height:150%"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;">（二）除综合柜员外其他岗位招聘单独进行，<span lang="EN-US">2017</span>年<span lang="EN-US">4</span>月底前完成第一批次人员评估工作。<b><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>

